name: Dilemma
description:
My friend was in a difficult situation when I took this shot. He was forced to make a difficult decision, he was in a dilemma, so he talked to me, and I ended up taking a picture of him and making a double exposure with a two-way road. I just turned the conversation into a picture!

Gear I used
Camera: Nikon FM10
Lens: 35~70 1:3.5~4.8
Film:Fujicolor C200

Technique: Double Exposure
